    "IoT security threats and attack surfaces are discussed.",
    "Among the potential surveyed applications, ML has been used mainly for intrusion detection, while DL for malware and anomalies detection.",
    "As main conclusions, the authors claim the need for diverse datasets within IoT security.",
    "The success of AI models depends merely on this.",
    "This is still an open issue due to the wide diversity of IoT devices in the ecosystem, as well as the privacy concerns related to critical information stored, such as industrial and medical data."
